# Bundles
LIFX Bundle Packs are your shortcut to instant atmosphere—no guesswork, just glow. Whether you're new to smart lighting or expanding your setup, each pack is curated to deliver a complete vibe straight out of the box. From the all-in Starter Kit and Switch Starter Kit (yes, you can keep the satisfying wall click), to the Bedroom Bundle for dreamy wind-downs and wake-ups.

## Products
* Starter Kit: $99.99
* Switch Starter Kit: $89.99

